Uttar Pradesh
Nov 26, 2014
Abduction, Rape
Description:
			A woman was allegedly raped by her husband and two of his friends in Bilaspur area, following which a case has been registered against the three.

The incident took place on November 17 when the woman was returning to her home here. She was abducted by her husband and his friends and taken to a secluded house in Bareilly, police said.

She was intoxicated through an injection, following which the three took turns to rape her.

The complainant and her husband have a strained relationship and have a domestic dispute case pending in the court, police added.

The victim managed to return to her home somehow, following which she filed an FIR against the three accused, they said.

Source: Press Trust of India